Interface ReplicatedRecordStore

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBaseReplicatedRecordStore, AbstractReplicatedRecordStore, DataReplicatedRecordStore, ObjectReplicatedRecordStorage

    public interface ReplicatedRecordStore
    This interface describes a common record store for replicated maps and their actual records
